    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You can use annotate your method with <code>@Scheduled(cron =\"0 1 1 * * ?\")</code>.</p>\n\n<p>0 - is for seconds</p>\n\n<p>1- 1 minute</p>\n\n<p>1 - hour of the day.</p>\n"
