    "question_id" : 26147044,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>One thing i've noticed is: spring CronTrigger is not cron. You may end up with 7 parameters in a valid cron expression (wich you can validate on cronmaker.com) and then spring not accept it. Most of cases you just delete the last parameter and everything works fine.</p>\n"
