    "body" : "<p>Spring cron expression for every day 1:01:am</p>\n\n<p>@Scheduled(cron = \"0 1 1 ? * *\")</p>\n\n<p>for more information check this information:</p>\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/cd/E12058_01/doc/doc.1014/e12030/cron_expressions.htm\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">https://docs.oracle.com/cd/E12058_01/doc/doc.1014/e12030/cron_expressions.htm</a></em></p>\n"
